Using the debugger:

1. Add a breakpoint - where we want to stop
  - Two ways to do that:
    1 - On the left side line number right click -> Select Breakpoint -> Toggle line breakpoint
    2 - On the line -> Debug -> Toggle line breakpoint (Ctrl + F8)
  - Then Debug -> Debug Project (Ctrl + F)
2. Start Debugger shortcut - Ctrl + F5
